var predEngine = mlContext.Model.CreatePredictionEngine<TaxiTrip, TaxiTripFarePrediction>(trainedModel); 
```
<---_this call_

throws a _System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException_ - Features column 'Feature' not found by_  <mlContext.Model.CreatePredictionEngine>

Could you ask what wrong I did with the retraining?
